::Aerotaur::
       He grunts his respect for having been able to catch his wrist.  
Leaning back he braces his legs against Wolfenstein's chest plate and 
switches the staff to his other hand.  Grabbing on to Wolfenstein's wrist 
with his captured hand swipes his bladed staff at Wolfenstein's head.
